<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6530711>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Pictures in life of (A) Lobulia brongersmai (BPBM 34733); (B) Lobulia elegans (BPBM 18692); (C) Lobulia fortis (paratype; BPBM 41130); (D) Lobulia huonensis (holotype; BPBM 40322); (E) Lobulia lobulus (BPBM 47837); (F) Lobulia marmorata (holotype; BPBM 34150). Images A, B, F by Fred Kraus, images C–E by Allen Allison." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6530711/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6530713>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Lobulia lobulus holotype (MCZ R-47067), in (A) dorsal view, (B) ventral view, (C) lateral view of head, (D) dorsal view of head and (E) ventral view of head. Images by Museum of Comparative Zoology, Harvard University." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6530713/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

